  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Namikaze clan members speed and agility allows them to better protect themselves from harm. </p><p>Beginning at 1st level if you are wearing Light or Medium Armor, you gain a +1 bonus to your Dexterity saving throws. </p><p>This increases to +2 at 11th level. Additionally, while you are concentrating on a Namikaze Clan Hijutsu, a creatures first attack against you per turn, is made at disadvantage.</p><p>Beginning at 15th level, when you would be forced to make a Dexterity saving throw to take half damage, you can choose to succeed instead, taking no damage or any adverse effects. You can only use this effect of Evasive Nature twice per long rest.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
